WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:01.705
<i>Previously on The Borgias...</i>

00:01.825 --> 00:04.526
May I present
Don Hernando de Caballos.

00:04.593 --> 00:06.190
He was at
the Siege of Granada.

00:06.191 --> 00:07.983
We had a siege in mind.

00:08.141 --> 00:10.951
Catherina Sforza,
has been threatening war.

00:10.952 --> 00:14.539
Give us occasion to
to bend her knee to Rome.

00:14.741 --> 00:17.077
Grab the boy!
Grab the boy!

00:17.705 --> 00:19.296
Here is your son!

00:19.558 --> 00:21.459
He is waiting to die!

00:22.135 --> 00:24.947
I have the means to
produce TEN MORE SONS!

00:25.408 --> 00:26.836
Madame,
may I present my brother,

00:26.837 --> 00:29.088
<i>Calvino Pallavicini da Genova.</i>

00:29.375 --> 00:31.543
Lady.
I am honoured.

00:31.812 --> 00:33.651
It's the brother, yes?

00:33.660 --> 00:34.755
Why not?

00:34.835 --> 00:36.169
Your father will never agree.

00:36.628 --> 00:39.411
You are marrying
for all of us, Lucrezia,

00:39.412 --> 00:40.571
not just yourself.

00:40.572 --> 00:41.472
For family!

00:41.473 --> 00:43.140
Girolamo Savonarola!

00:43.265 --> 00:44.405
This edict finds
you guilty

00:44.406 --> 00:46.276
of disseminating
pernicious doctrines.

00:46.277 --> 00:47.558
You are hereby ordered

00:47.559 --> 00:49.592
to suspend your
sermons and prophecies.

00:49.670 --> 00:51.322
I will use it...

00:51.409 --> 00:53.555
...to wipe my ass!

00:54.287 --> 00:56.442
We have one among us
who would be a martyr.

00:57.049 --> 00:58.982
Take note of the man
with the water jug.

00:59.423 --> 01:02.058
He's the pope's taster.

01:02.126 --> 01:05.428
Ludovico of Milan is
marching on Forli.

01:05.495 --> 01:06.763
Could a messenger
reach my brother

01:06.864 --> 01:08.031
in time to warn him?

01:08.099 --> 01:09.318
That would depend

01:09.386 --> 01:11.916
on how fast the messenger
chooses to ride.

01:12.017 --> 01:14.548
We are under attack!

01:14.615 --> 01:16.011
Kill the boy!

01:16.113 --> 01:17.278
Hang him!

01:17.379 --> 01:18.710
Yah!

